title: Portage Park / Jefferson Park 3 bed 1 bath available 7/1
app_fee: $47 includes credit check, financial check, and criminal background check
posting_body: ['Border of Portage Park and Jefferson Park, sun-drenched top-floor 3-bedroom apartment in vintage two flat on a double lot.', 'Well maintained unit with a brand new bathroom (never used, not pictured) and fresh paint.', 'Kitchen includes dishwasher (not pictured).', 'Large yard and communal patio space.', 'Central AC and heat.', 'Owners live onsite on the first floor.', 'Available as soon as 7/1.', 'Easy non-permit street parking (free) and garage parking (for additional $50 a month) are available.', 'Quiet, tree-lined street close to transportation and the six corners of Portage Park.', 'Walking distance to the Jefferson Park L, UP-NW Metra, and MD-N Metra and close to highway.', 'No smoking in building and no pets.', 'Rental application fee of $47 includes credit check and background check.', "Renters must maintain renter's insurance"]
